Module kivakit.core.serialization.kryo

Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.serialization.kryo

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoreKernelKryoTypes
    Kryo types to register for kivakit-core-kernel
    DebugKryo
    Not public API
    KryoSerializationSession
    An extension of the Kryo object which adds enhanced reading and writing capabilities and enforces versioning of all data that is read or written, according to the SerializationSession contract.
    KryoSerializer<Value>
    Kryo serializer extension class for serializing a particular type of object.
    KryoTypeEntry
    Not public API
    KryoTypes
    A set of Kryo type registrations required to construct a KryoSerializationSession.
    KryoUnitTest
    Adds Kryo serialization testing to the UnitTest base class.
